The paper describes a robot system that uses computer vision and AI techniques to automate pick and place operations in unstructured environments, specifically the shelves in an Amazon warehouse. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
